## Project Structure

```
cf-cache-audit/
├── cf_cache_audit/
│   ├── __init__.py         # Package metadata
│   ├── __main__.py         # python -m entry point
│   ├── cli.py              # CLI argument parsing & orchestration
│   ├── crawler.py          # Async website crawler
│   ├── analyzer.py         # Cache status validation & warm-cache testing
│   ├── cloudflare.py       # Cloudflare & CDN detection
│   ├── reporter.py         # Rich terminal output & JSON/CSV export
│   ├── models.py           # Pydantic models & enumerations
│   └── utils.py            # URL helpers, classification, rate limiter
├── tests/
│   ├── test_models.py      # Model & serialisation tests
│   ├── test_utils.py       # URL normalisation, classification tests
│   ├── test_cloudflare.py  # Header detection tests
│   ├── test_crawler.py     # HTML parsing & framework detection tests
│   └── test_analyzer.py    # Summary computation tests
├── pyproject.toml          # PEP 621 project configuration
├── requirements.txt        # Dependency pins
└── README.md               # This file
```

